entries.femaleVariant: We should get a move on soon. We camp out any longer, we'll start growing roots.
What, had enough of the view?
Come on. Windmills to the left, windmills to the right. Be nice to see some mountains for a change.
Could head out to Appalachia. They say the radiation's gone down.
Tell you what, I could stand to go on a little loot run.
I could do anything, long as it's away from these windmills.
